high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink in front of you
Pick up the sponge that is sitting inside the sink
Turn around and walk to the bathtub
Place the sponge in the bathtub to the right of the soap
Turn around and walk to the door then turn left and walk to the cabinets
Open the bottom right cabinet and pick up the sponge then close the cabinet
Turn around and walk to the bathtub
Place the sponge in the bathtub in between the soap and other sponge.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the sponge in the sink.
Turn around and go to the bathtub.
Put the sponge in the bathtub.
Turn around and go to the cabinets by the sink.
Take out the sponge from the bottom cabinets.
Turn around and go to the bathtub.
Put the sponge in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the sponge out of the sink basin.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right again and walk up to the end of the tub.
Place the sponge vertically into the tub.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then hang a left and walk up to the cupboards.
Open the bottom right cupboard and take a sponge out of the cupboard, then close the door.
Turn around and walk over to the ed of the tub.
Place the sponge into the tub vertically to the right of the soap.
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to the tub.

high_descs: Turn left twice and walk to the sink.
Pick up the green sponge That is in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the bathtub.
Place the sponge in the sink to the right of the pink soap.
Turn around and go to the far right cabinet.
Open the lower far right cabinet and take out the green sponge on the shelf.
Turn around and go to the bathtub.
Place the sponge in the bathtub to the left of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put two green sponges in the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn and move to the sink.
Pick up the green dish sponge from the sink.
Carry the green sponge to the bath tub.
Place the green sponge in the bath tub.
Move to the cupboards that are to the right of the sink.
Open the bottom right cupboard and remove the green sponge that's inside it.
Carry the green sponge to the bath tub.
Place the sponge next to the other sponge you already put in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two green sponges to the bath tub.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the toilet
Pick up sponge from the sink
Move to the tub behind you
Put the sponge in the tub
Move to the cabinet to the right of you
Pick up sponge from the cabinet
Move to the tub behind you
Put the sponge in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges in the tub.
